room_title: Escape room "The Mystery of Stillwater Asylum" by Kryptic Tales in Orange County
room_description:
A string of people have gone missing in the area and the Zodiac Killer is still at large! As amateur detectives, you’ve received a mysterious letter on your desk with a single word... “STILLWATER”, the name of an old, abandoned asylum at the far edge of town.

With your new lead, you and your team head to the asylum looking for answers...but what you find may be more than you bargained for...
